Description:
    - Generator, which handle dynamics descriptions and link the parameter angle of first phong tag from the generator.

Class/method highlighted:
    - c4d.plugins.ObjectData
    - NodeData.Init()
    - NodeData.CopyTo()
    - NodeData.Read()
    - NodeData.Write()
    - NodeData.GetDDescription()
